Maintainer: Christian Eichert <c@zp1.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), apache2-dev, libapr1-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/ecxod/mod_mermaid

Package: mod-mermaid
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, apache2 (>= 2.4), nodejs, npm, chromium
Description: Apache module for rendering Mermaid diagrams
 mod_mermaid is an Apache module that dynamically renders Mermaid diagram
 files (.mmd) as SVG in the browser. It uses the Mermaid CLI (mmdc) to
 convert diagrams on-the-fly, requiring no caching or additional tools.